    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it\u2019s been pampered since day one and kept tucked away in a garage. It drives like a total dream and is sparkling clean inside and out. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
