    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, an analog masterpiece in flawless condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double-VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. With factory-spec suspension geometry and a pristine chassis, this M3 delivers the precise lateral dynamics and linear power delivery synonymous with the 'M' badge. A turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
