    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition that must be seen to be fully appreciated. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a soft cover. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the factory; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases, while the carpets and dashboard are pristine. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a meticulous folder of dealership service records and a documented history of preventative maintenance. It delivers a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet, just as it was on day one. This is an investment-grade example intended for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. The sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
